细胞自然衰亡，有效杀死癌细胞。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (三)朴菇多糖，临床研究证实对小鼠肿瘤S180，肝癌22（H22）、Lewis肺癌和艾氏腹水瘤（EC）具有明显的杀灭作用。它能使癌组织坏死增加，糖元减少，对瘤组织的非特异酯酶有显著的抑制增殖功效。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; （四）有机锗可以从癌细胞中夺取电子，使其电位下降，可以把不正常电位调整成正常电位，消除体内的癌电位，还能抑制癌基因DNA的复制，从而达到抑制癌细胞繁殖并防止其向它处扩散的功效。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; （五）粘多糖还可以使肿瘤纤维细胞增加，穿透肿瘤，并把肿瘤分割包裹。一方面进一步阻止了肿瘤扩散；另一方面可使大量免疫细胞更易于集中对抗癌细胞。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; （六）朴菇素Ⅱ及锗—复合朴菇多糖络合物、核酸、锗一多糖等能全面迅速激活人体的免疫功能,增加免疫细胞（天然杀伤细胞NK,杀伤细胞K,巨噬细胞M及肿瘤坏死因子TNF、白介素—2（IL—2）的数量，提高它们杀伤癌细胞的能力，达到清除残余癌细胞，阻断其转移、扩散、复发,修复免疫细胞,重筑健康屏障的目的；同时修复肝损伤及受损基因,保护骨髓造血功能。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; （七）朴菇蛋白多糖（朴菇素Ⅲ)增加肿瘤杀伤细胞的活性,促进抗体的产生。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; （八)有效控制<a href=\"http://www.zlxty.com/ypjs.asp?id=1047\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;color:#FF0000;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;\">癌症引发的疼痛</a>。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 内啡肽能使疼痛消失,就好象人体内的吗啡。但内啡肽在体内易于分解，很难保留，因此人们便会感到疼痛。而金菌灵胶囊中的锗—复合朴菇多糖络合物的作用就是防止内啡肽分解,使其长期保留在体内,从而起到止痛的作用。&nbsp;</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">【适应症】早、中、晚期各种类型的恶性肿瘤。适用于手术前后、放化疗当中、放化疗后、重症晚期病人及痛疼病人。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">【用法用量】1次4粒，1日2次，空腹口服。加量服用：1次6粒，1天3次或1次4粒，1天3次。本品有量效关系，量越大效果越好。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 如果有吞咽困难，可将胶囊里的粉溶于水中服用。病性较重及初次服用的患者，第一个大周期（三个疗程）应酌情加量。随机对照临床试验结果表明：本品量效关系明显。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">【不良反应】本品无不良反应。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">【禁忌症】本品无禁忌症。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 经临床验证，大洋扶生金菌灵胶囊是目前抑瘤率高、无任何毒副作用、安全高效的广谱抗肿瘤药物。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">大洋扶生金菌灵胶囊临床应用</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">■手术前服用</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 术前服用“大洋扶生”可以高效抑杀癌细胞，防止癌细胞的扩散和转移。多家医院临床表明，它能使瘤体表面大面积坏死,有利于手术，并可以术前控制病情进展。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">■术后服用</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 可杀死体内残余的癌细胞，消灭手术不能消除的病灶,并防止复发、扩散、转移。有利于术后伤口愈合,恢复病人体力。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">■联合放疗</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 配合放疗，可使放疗剂量减少，疗效增强，副作用显著降低。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">■联合化疗</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 大量临床实验表明：“大洋扶生”联合化疗可显著提高化疗的疗效,还可以降低化疗药物的剂量,另外原先对化疗药物不敏感的肿瘤,服用“大洋扶生”后可使化疗敏感，即增敏作用；同时“大洋扶生”还可以防止化疗药物引起的一系列毒副作用,保护病人的骨髓造血机能、肝脏、肾脏、心肌免受化疗药物的损害，即减毒作用。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">■放、化疗后服用</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 放、化疗不能完全清除癌细胞，经过放、化疗，残余的癌细胞具备更强的生长特性,更易增殖、复发。化疗还容易使癌细胞多极分化，变异生成更不易控制的变异细胞。多数化疗药物具有这种突变作用。所以说，化疗不但治癌还可以致癌。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 放、化疗后及时服用“大洋扶生”重筑遭受重创的免疫系统,修复免疫细胞,加强病人内在的抗癌力量；同时杀灭放、化疗后残余的癌细胞、突变细胞,防止残余的癌细胞卷土重来。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">■急、重、晚期服用</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 急、重、晚期或不能手术、放化疗的病人服用，可抑制肿瘤增殖，控制转移，扩散；同时明显改善临床症状如食欲、睡眠、体力等；改善胸腹水,黄疸、衰竭等恶病质；明显缓解疼痛，从而提高病人生存质量，延长生命。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 大量临床实验和数十万患者应用疗效表明：大洋扶生金菌灵胶囊对肝癌、肺癌、胃癌、食管癌、大肠癌、淋巴癌、鼻咽癌、脑肿瘤、乳腺癌、子宫癌、卵巢癌、前列腺癌、膀胱癌、胰腺癌、甲状腺癌、喉癌、神经细胞瘤、黑色素瘤、骨癌、皮肤癌、睾丸癌、白血病和转移癌等各种肿瘤具有显著的双项抗癌综合治疗效果，适合于早、中、晚期各种类型的癌症患者。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">●“大洋扶生”已成功应用于国内及美国、日本、韩国、德国、泰国、香港、台湾、印尼等海内外恶性肿瘤患者数十万例。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:Verdana;\">●大洋扶生金菌灵胶囊的研制成功引起了国内外医学界和媒体的广泛关注——欧洲生物化学杂志、日本癌症研究杂志、英国药物代谢杂志、美国国立医学图书馆资料（从互联网上下载）等都对它进行了高度评价。</span>\r\n									</p>\r\n								</div>\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n					</tbody>\r\n				</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>','消癌平胶囊','上海悦胜芜湖药业有限公司','0.25g*36粒','盒','国药准字Z2005072','YPBH898')
INSERT INTO `dy_product_field` VALUES('22','用药说明：<br />\r\n迪恩安&nbsp;<br />\r\n适应症： 1.病毒性疾病：伴有HBV-DNA 、DNA多聚酶阳性或HBeAg阳性等病毒复制标志的成年慢性活动性.乙型肝炎乙型肝炎病人、伴有HCV抗体阳性和谷丙转氨酶（ALT）增高，但不伴有肝功能代偿失调（Child分类A）的成年急慢性丙型肝炎病人、尖锐湿疣、带状疱疹、小儿病毒性肺炎及上呼吸道感染、慢性宫颈炎、丁型肝炎等。 2.肿瘤：毛状细胞白血病、多发性骨髓瘤、非何杰金氏淋巴瘤、慢性白血病以及卡波济氏肉瘤、肾癌、喉乳头状瘤、黑色素瘤、蕈样肉芽肿、膀胱癌、基底细胞癌等。<br />\r\n用法用量<br />\r\n1.毛状细胞白血病起始剂量：每日300万国际单位，皮下或肌内注射，16到24周。如耐受性差，则应将每日剂量减少到150万国际单位，或将用药次数改为每周3次，也可以同时减少剂量和用药次数。维持剂量：每次300万国际单位，每周3次皮下或肌内注射。如耐受性差，则将每日剂量减少到150万国际单位，每周3次。<br />\r\n　　疗程：应用该药大约6个月以后，再由医生决定是否对疗效良好的病人继续用药或是对疗效不佳的病人终止用药。<br />\r\n　　注：对血小板减少症病人（血小板计数少于50×109/L）或有出血危险的病人，建议以皮下注射重组人干扰素α2a。<br />\r\n　　2. 多发性骨髓瘤应用重组人干扰素α2a300万国际单位，每周3次皮下或肌内注射。根据不同病人的耐受性，可将剂量逐周增加至最大耐收量（900万国际单位）每周3次。除病情迅速发展或耐受性极差外，这一剂量可持续使用。<br />\r\n　　3.低度恶性非何杰金氏淋巴瘤重组人干扰素α2a作为化疗的辅助治疗（伴随或不伴随放疗），可以延长低度恶性非何杰金氏淋巴瘤病人的无病生存期和无恶化生存期。推荐剂量：在常规化疗结束后（伴随或不伴随放疗），每周3次，每次300万国际单位，皮下注射重组人干扰素α2a，至少维持治疗12周。重组人干扰素α2a的治疗应该在病人从化—放疗反应中一恢复立即开始，一般时间为化—放疗后4～6周。重组人干扰素α2a治疗也可伴随常规的化疗方案（如结合环磷酰胺、强的松、长春新碱和阿霉素）一起进行。以28天为一周期。在第22～26天，皮下或肌内注射重组人干扰素α2a600万国际单位/m2体表面积。重组人干扰素α2a结合化疗进行治疗时，重组人干扰素α2a的使用应该和化疗同时进行。<br />\r\n　　4.慢性髓性白血病重组人干扰素α2a适用于慢性髓性白血病病人。60%处于慢性期的慢性髓性白血病病人，不管是否接受其他治疗，接受重组人干扰素α2a治疗后可达到血液学缓解。三分之二这类病人在开始接受治疗最近18个月后取得完全的血液学缓解。与细胞毒性化疗不同，重组人干扰素α2a能持续维持细胞遗传学缓解达40个月以上。<br />\r\n　　推荐剂量：建议对年满18岁或以上的病人作重组人干扰素α2a皮下或肌内注射8～12周，<br />\r\n　　推荐逐渐增加剂量的方案如下：第1～3天　每日300万国际单位；第4～6天　每日600万国际单位；第7～84天　每日900万国际单位<br />\r\n　　疗程：病人必须接受治疗至少8周，要取得更好的疗效至少需要治疗12周，然后，再由医生决定是否对疗效良好的病人继续用药或对血液学参数未见任何改善者终止用药。疗效良好的病人应继续用药，直至取得完全的血液学缓解，或者一直用药最多到18个月。所有达到完全血液学缓解的病人，均应继续以每日900万国际单位（最佳剂量）或以900万国际单位每周3次（最低剂量）进行治疗，以使其在尽可能短的时间内取得细胞遗传学缓解。尽管有见到开始治疗2年后达到细胞遗传学缓解者，但尚未定出重组人干扰素α2a治疗慢性髓性白血病的最佳疗程。<br />\r\n　　5.慢性活动性乙型肝炎重组人干扰素α2a适合治疗伴有HBV—DNA、HbeAg及DNA多聚酶阳性等病毒复制标志的成年慢性活动性乙型肝炎<br />\r\n　　推荐剂量：尚未定出治疗慢性活动性乙型肝炎的最佳治疗方案。通常以500万国际单位每周3次，皮下注射，共用6个月。如用药一个月后病毒复制标志或HbeAg无下降，则可逐渐加大剂量并可进一步将剂量调整至病人能够耐受的水平，如治疗3～4个月后没有改善，则应考虑停止治疗.<br />\r\n　　儿童：据报道对患有慢性乙型肝炎的儿童以每平方米体表面积1000万国际单位进行治疗是安全的，但其治疗效果尚未定论。<br />\r\n　　警告：重组人干扰素α2a对慢性乙型肝炎合并感染人类免疫缺陷病毒（HIV）的病人疗效尚无定论。<br />\r\n　　6.急慢性丙型肝炎重组人干扰素α2a适合治疗HCV抗体阳性，谷丙转氨酶（ALT）增高和不伴肝脏失代偿成年慢性丙型肝炎病人。但没有临床和组织学方面长期好转的依据。<br />\r\n　　起始剂量：以重组人干扰素α2a300～500万国际单位，每周3次，皮下或肌内注射3个月作为诱导治疗。<br />\r\n　　维持剂量：血清谷丙转氨酶正常的病人需要再以重组人干扰素α2a300万国际单位，每周3次，注射3个月作为完全缓解的巩固治疗。病人血清谷丙转氨酶不正常者必须停止以重组人干扰素α2a治疗。<br />\r\n　　注：大多数接受了足够治疗后复发的病人会在治疗结束后4个月内复发。<br />\r\n　　7.尖锐湿疣以重组人干扰素α2a100～300万国际单位，每周3次，皮下或肌内注射，共1至2个月。或于患处基底部隔日注射100万国际单位，连续3周。<br />\r\n不良反应<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 使用本品后少数病人可有发烧、寒战、乏力、肌痛、厌食等反应。不良反应多在注射48小时后消失。其他可能出现的不良反应有头痛、关节痛、食欲不振、恶心等，个别病人可能出现粒性白细胞减少、血小板减少等，停药后可恢复。如出现不能忍受的严重不良反应时，应减少剂量或停药，并给予必要的对症治疗。<br />\r\n禁忌：<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 1.对重组人干扰素α2a或该制剂的任何成分有过敏史者。<br />\r\n　　2.患有严重心脏疾病或有心脏病史者。<br />\r\n　　3.严重的肝、肾或骨髓功能不正常者。<br />\r\n　　4.癫痫及中枢神经系统功能损伤者。<br />\r\n　　5.伴有晚期失代偿性肝病或肝硬化的肝炎患者。<br />\r\n　　6.正在接受或近期内接受免疫抑制剂治疗的慢性肝炎患者，短期“去激素”治疗者除外。<br />\r\n　　7.即将接受同种异体骨髓移植的HLA抗体识别相关的慢性髓性白血病病人。<br />','a-2a干扰素','辽宁卫星生物制品研究所(有限公司)','100万单位','盒','国药准字S10980085','YPBH1203')
INSERT INTO `dy_product_field` VALUES('23','<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">用药说明</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-indent:5.145pt;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">枫苓合剂</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">——</span><a href=\"http://www.zlxty.com/Zlzt.asp?page=1\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;text-decoration:none;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;color:#FF0000;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">胃癌、肠癌、肝癌</span></a><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">、胰腺癌、食道癌等消化系统肿瘤新药</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　国内第一个消化系统</span><a href=\"http://www.zlxty.com/\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;text-decoration:none;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;color:#FF0000;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">肿瘤</span></a><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">治疗性中药，</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">54</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">位专家</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">18</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">年的潜心研究</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　上海市重大科技项目医保用药，拥有两项专利和自主知识产权</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">有效改善临床症状和体征，显著抑杀癌细胞，提高患者生存质量</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　我国在自主知识产权的抗癌药物研发方面又取得了重要突破，专门用于胃癌等消化系统肿瘤的治疗性药物</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">—“</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">枫苓合剂</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">”</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">在上海成功上市。枫苓合剂经原国家卫生部批准，经全国十二个省级医院的临床试验、验证，疗效优于化疗，达到了国内领先、国际先进的水平，被列为我国第一个治疗性的抗癌中成药。原材料在国内可采购，项目拥有专利，经批准，获新药证书。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　本药物对胃癌、肝癌、肠癌为主的消化系统癌症，具有明显的治疗效果，同时又无明显的毒副反应，尤其是对人体胃癌</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">MKN</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">的抑瘤率达到</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">80%</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">以上。能明显缩小肿瘤，解除肿瘤患者的病痛，显著提高生存质量，延长患者的生命，为肿瘤患者开辟了一条新的治疗途径。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">1</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">、治疗功能：</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　主治胃癌、肠癌、肝癌、胰腺癌、食道癌等消化系统肿瘤。也可以用与肺癌、乳腺癌、宫颈癌和脑部肿瘤等其他癌症状，对不宜放化疗的患者疗效尤其显著。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">2</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">、临床试验</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　全国多家权威知名肿瘤医院，临床试验长达</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">7</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">年、</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">600</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">例大样本、</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">3000</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">例临床验证。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">3</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">、治疗缓解率</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　临床总缓解率高达</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">26.4%</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">，超过国家标准</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">3.3</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">倍，高于临床对照化疗组</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">11</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">倍。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">4</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">、疗效有效率</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　临床总有效率高达</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">93.2%</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">，对比化疗组总有效率</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">71.4%</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">，高于对照化疗组有效率</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">21.8%</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">5</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">、治疗安全度</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　安全度高于同比化疗组</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">4.66</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">倍，有效服用计量仅为有毒剂量的</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">1/250</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">6</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">、治疗方法</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">—</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">单独治疗、与化疗合并治疗</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">7</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">、临床治疗效果：</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　近期效果：改善症状。患者服用</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">3-15</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">天内，诸如癌症疼痛、饮食障碍、胸腹水等症状即可得到明显改善。中期效果：提高免疫。患者服用</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">1-2</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">个月后，可以有效提升白细胞，具有较明显的调整免疫、刺激骨髓造血效果，对正在放化疗的患者，更具有显著的增效减毒作用。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　远期效果：抑杀肿瘤。服用</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">2-3</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">疗程（</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">4-6</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">个月）后，可有效控制癌灶大小，抑制癌细胞活性，逐渐灭杀肿瘤。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【品　名】枫苓合剂</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【汉语拼音】</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">Fengling&nbsp;Heji</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【主要成份】大风子、大鳖子、大黄、甘草等。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【性　状】本品为棕褐色液体：气微香，味甜。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【药理作用】</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　临床前药效学试验表明，本品对体外培养的人子宫颈癌细胞（</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">Hela</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">）、肝癌细胞（</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">7704</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">）、胃癌细胞（</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">7901</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">）、肺腺癌细胞（</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">Al</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">）的生长具有抑制作用；本品口服或腹腔注射给药，对</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">C26</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">小鼠移植性结肠癌、小鼠</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">Lewis</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">肺癌及人体肝癌异种移植和模型</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">MKN</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">及人体肝癌异种移植模型</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">QFY</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">均有一定的抑瘤作用，口服药对小鼠移植性</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">S180</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">肉瘤和</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">H22</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">肝癌也具有抑制作用；本品还可促进小鼠腹腔巨噬细胞的吞噬功能，增加荷</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">Lewis</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">肺癌小鼠机体</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">NK</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">细胞活力。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【功能主治】</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　攻毒散积、活血行淤。适用不宜手术、放化疗的晚期淤毒结滞证胃癌。本品与化疗药合用，对淤毒结滞证胃癌的化疗、淤毒结滞证原发性肝癌介入加栓化疗有一定增效作用。有改善临床症状、生存质量作用。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【用法用量】</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　口服，每次</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">15ml</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">，每日</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">2</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">次。疗程</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">2</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">个月。原发性肝癌与介入加栓塞化疗合用时，在介入化疗前一周开始服用本品；胃癌与化疗合用时，与化疗同时开始服用本品。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【规　格】两种规格：</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">100ml/</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">瓶；</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">15ml*10</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">支</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">/</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">盒</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【包　装】棕色药用聚酯瓶，每盒装</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">1</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">瓶；棕色玻璃管制药瓶，每盒装</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">10</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">支。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【有</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">效</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">期】</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">24</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">个月</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【批准文号】国药准字</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">Z20053611</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【生产企业】上海百棵药业有限公司</span> \r\n</p>','枫苓合剂','上海百棵药业有限公司','100ml','瓶','国药准字Z20053611','YPBH1160')
INSERT INTO `dy_product_field` VALUES('24','<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">用药说明</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">：</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">复方木鸡颗粒</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://www.zlxty.com/ypml2.asp?scid=1&amp;skey=%B8%B4%B7%BD%C4%BE%BC%A6\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;text-decoration:none;\">复方木鸡</a></span>颗粒做为肝病良药被医药界誉为癌前阻断剂。并得到国家、省、市有关部门的高度重视。<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">2001</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">年</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">11</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">月，复方木鸡颗粒系列产品的开发与应用被国家计委评为国家现代中药高技术产业化示范工程，重点扶持。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　该产品所采用的超临界</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">CO2</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">萃取技术在国际上属领先水平。该系列品种对甲胎蛋白（</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">AFP</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">）的独特疗效属国内首创，它的开发与应用填补了国内同类产品的空白，为千万肝病及肿瘤患者带来了福音。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">[21]</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">复方木鸡颗粒由云芝提取物、山豆根、菟丝子、核桃楸皮等组成。木鸡的主要成分云芝多糖具有提高非特异性细胞免疫功能，对吞噬细胞、</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">T</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">细胞，特别是辅助性</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">T</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">细胞有刺激作用。菟丝子具有滋养肝肾之功效，能激活非特异性细胞的活性，此两味药恰有中医所认为的</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">“</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">扶正</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">”</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">的作用。而核桃楸皮、山豆根的主要成分是蓖醌类及生物碱类化合物，具有清热解毒、散肿瘤之功效，正是起到了</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">“</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">祛</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">”</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">的作用，因此具有</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">“</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">扶正不留邪，祛邪不伤正</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">”</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">的功效。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　研究结果显示，本品对小鼠肉瘤</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">180</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">有一定的抑制作用，对荷瘤小鼠细胞免疫功能有所提高；对四氯化碳所致大鼠血清转氨酶升高有所降低。并且该药能提高</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">T</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">细胞的免疫活性，提高巨噬细胞的吞噬能力，对机体内环境起着综合性的调节作用。通过动物实验证明，复方木鸡颗粒对化疗药物有明显的减毒作用，且具有较强的抗癌活性，用到临床可以作为一种化疗药物的减毒手段和抗癌免疫增强剂，二者联合应用，可以明显提高癌症患者的治疗效果。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　因此国家中药品种保护评审专家指出，复方木鸡颗粒剂做为一种癌前阻断剂，具有抑制甲胎蛋白升高的作用，对肝炎、肝硬化、肝癌患者具有明显的疗效。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【药品名称】：复方木鸡颗粒</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【性　状】：本品为褐色的颗粒；味微苦</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【成　份】：云芝提取物、核桃楸皮、山豆根、菟丝子。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【药理作用】：临床前动物实验结果提示：本品对小鼠肉瘤</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">180</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">有一定　的抑制作用；对荷瘤小鼠细胞免疫功能有所提高；对四　氢化碳所致大鼠血清转氨酶升高有所降低。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【功能主治】：具有抑制甲胎蛋白升高的作用。用于肝炎，肝硬化，</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://www.zlxty.com/zls.asp?id=32\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;color:#555555;text-decoration:none;\">肝癌</a></span>。<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【用法用量】：口服，一次</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">10g</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">，一日</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">3</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">次。饭后服。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【贮　藏】：密封。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【规　格】：4</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">g*9</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">袋</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;\">/</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">合；复和膜包装。</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">【有效期　】：三年</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;padding:0px;border:0px;color:#666666;font-family:宋体, Arial;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:13.5pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">　　【生产企业】：丹东药业集团有限公司</span>\r\n</p>','复方木鸡颗粒','丹东药业集团有限公司','4g*9袋','盒','国药准字Z21020413','YPBH1221')
